---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Hamshiralar uchun — Clary"
  description="Sertifikatli hamshiralar uchun: moslashuvchan jadval, klinika hamkorligi, to'g'ridan-to'g'ri to'lov. Ilovani yuklang."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 h-[420px] w-[420px] rounded-full bg-emerald-500/15 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/3 -right-24 h-[420px] w-[420px] rounded-full bg-teal-500/10 blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto grid gap-12 px-4 py-20 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border/60 bg-background/80 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium">
          <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500"></span>
          Hamshiralar uchun
        </div>
        <h1 class="mt-5 text-balance text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
          Vazifalar oling, daromad qiling
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-5 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
          Sertifikatlangan hamshiralar uchun platforma. Klinikalar va bemorlardan ish so'rovlari oling,
          o'z jadvalingizni boshqaring va to'g'ridan-to'g'ri to'lov oling.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=uz.clary.nurse" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-black px-5 py-2.5 text-white hover:opacity-90">
            <svg class="h-7 w-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M3.6 2.1c-.3.3-.5.7-.5 1.3v17.2c0 .6.2 1 .5 1.3l.1.1L13 12.5v-.2L3.7 2l-.1.1z"/><path d="M16.2 15.7l-3.2-3.2v-.2l3.2-3.2.1.1L20 11.4c1.1.6 1.1 1.6 0 2.2l-3.7 2.1-.1.1z"/><path d="M16.3 15.6L13 12.4 3.6 21.9c.4.4 1 .4 1.7.1l11-6.4"/><path d="M16.3 9.2l-11-6.3c-.7-.4-1.3-.4-1.7.1L13 12.4l3.3-3.2z"/></svg>
            <div class="text-left leading-tight">
              <div class="text-[10px] uppercase opacity-80">Get it on</div>
              <div class="text-base font-semibold">Google Play</div>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="https://apps.apple.com/uz/app/clary-nurse/id000000" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl bg-black px-5 py-2.5 text-white hover:opacity-90">
            <svg class="h-7 w-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16.5 12.5c0-2.6 2.1-3.8 2.2-3.9-1.2-1.7-3-2-3.7-2-1.6-.2-3 .9-3.8.9-.8 0-2-.9-3.3-.9-1.7 0-3.3 1-4.1 2.5-1.8 3-.5 7.5 1.3 10 .9 1.2 1.9 2.5 3.2 2.5 1.3-.1 1.8-.8 3.3-.8 1.6 0 2 .8 3.3.8 1.4 0 2.3-1.2 3.1-2.4.7-.9 1.2-1.9 1.5-2.9-1.5-.6-3-2.1-3-3.8zM14 4.4c.7-.9 1.2-2.1 1.1-3.4-1.1.1-2.4.7-3.1 1.6-.7.8-1.3 2-1.1 3.2 1.2 0 2.4-.6 3.1-1.4z"/></svg>
            <div class="text-left leading-tight">
              <div class="text-[10px] uppercase opacity-80">Download on the</div>
              <div class="text-base font-semibold">App Store</div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground">Yoki <a href="/signup?role=nurse" class="text-[#2563EB] hover:underline">Web orqali ro'yxatdan o'tish</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {[
          ['💼', 'Moslashuvchan ish'],
          ['💸', "To'g'ridan-to'g'ri to'lov"],
          ['⭐', "Reyting va sharhlar"],
          ['📅', 'O\'z jadvalingiz'],
        ].map(([i, t]) => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border bg-card p-5">
            <div class="text-2xl">{i}</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold">{t}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits -->
  <section class="bg-muted/20 py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Nega Clary?</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">Hamshiralar uchun afzalliklar</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {[
          ['🕒', "O'zingiz jadval tuzasiz", 'Qaysi kun, qaysi soatda ishlashni o\'zingiz hal qilasiz'],
          ['🏥', "Tasdiqlangan klinikalar", "Faqat tekshirilgan klinikalar bilan hamkorlik"],
          ['💳', "To'lov darhol", "Vazifa tugagandan keyin to'lov 24 soat ichida kartangizga"],
          ['📍', "Yaqin atrofdagi vazifalar", "Uyingizdan yaqin masofadagi mijozlarni topasiz"],
          ['🎓', "Onlayn o'qishlar", "Sertifikat va kasbiy rivojlanish kurslari"],
          ['🛡', "Sug'urta qoplamasi", "Ish davomidagi himoya — Clary tomonidan"],
        ].map(([icon, title, body]) => (
          <div class="card-hover rounded-lg border bg-card p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl">{icon}</div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 font-semibold">{title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">{body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Earnings -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl rounded-2xl border bg-card p-10">
        <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold">Qancha daromad qilishingiz mumkin?</h2>
        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
          {[
            ['Yarim kunlik', '3–5M', "so'm/oy"],
            ['To\'liq kunlik', '7–10M', "so'm/oy"],
            ['Premium', '12M+', "so'm/oy"],
          ].map(([t, a, p]) => (
            <div class="rounded-lg border bg-background p-6 text-center">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground">{t}</div>
              <div class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-600">{a}</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">{p}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-center text-xs text-muted-foreground">* Tajriba, joylashuv va ish hajmiga qarab o'zgaradi</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Requirements -->
  <section class="bg-muted/20 py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4">
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold">Kerakli hujjatlar</h2>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {[
          'Tibbiyot bilim yurti yoki universitet diplomi',
          'Hamshira sertifikati (amaldagi)',
          'Pasport yoki ID karta',
          'Tibbiyot ko\'rigi (oxirgi 6 oy)',
          'Telefon raqami va asosiy hisob raqam',
          '18 yoshdan katta',
        ].map((r) => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-lg border bg-card p-4">
            <span class="text-[#10B981]">&#10003;</span>
            <span class="text-sm">{r}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4">
      <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold">Hamshiralar bergan savollar</h2>
      <div class="mt-10 space-y-3">
        {[
          ["Ro'yxatdan o'tish bepulmi?", "Ha, mutlaqo bepul. Clary faqat har bir tugagan vazifadan kichik komissiya oladi."],
          ["Komissiya qancha?", "Vazifa qiymatining 10–15%. Bu marketing, sug'urta va to'lov xizmatlarini o'z ichiga oladi."],
          ["Vazifani rad eta olamanmi?", "Ha. Lekin doimiy rad etish reytingingizga ta'sir qiladi va kelajakdagi vazifalar kamayadi."],
          ["To'lov qachon keladi?", "Vazifa tugagach, mijoz tomonidan tasdiqlanganidan keyin 24 soat ichida kartangizga."],
          ["Sug'urta qoplamasi qanday ishlaydi?", "Har bir vazifa uchun avtomatik faollashadi. Tafsilotlar shartnomada."],
        ].map(([q, a]) => (
          <details class="group rounded-lg border bg-card p-4">
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between font-semibold">
              <span>{q}</span>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground group-open:rotate-180 transition">&darr;</span>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground">{a}</p>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl rounded-2xl border bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 p-10 text-center text-white shadow-xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Bugun jamoaga qo'shiling</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 opacity-90">Ariza topshirish 5 daqiqa, tasdiqlash 1–2 ish kuni</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
          <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=uz.clary.nurse" class="rounded-md bg-white px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 hover:bg-neutral-100">Google Play</a>
          <a href="https://apps.apple.com/uz/app/clary-nurse/id000000" class="rounded-md border border-white/40 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/10">App Store</a>
          <a href="/signup?role=nurse" class="rounded-md border border-white/40 px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/10">Web orqali</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
